snippet.title: Restaurant City by Playfish
snippet.description:
Play now at http://apps.facebook.com/restaurantcity

In Restaurant City you get to create and run your very own restaurant! Design it, decorate it, hire your friends to work in it, collect new ingredients and menu items and visit friends! Will you be the next Restaurant Mogul? Join million of players and start your own restaurant today at http://www.playfish.com/restaurantcity
